                      <h1 class="title">
              Publications            </h1>
                    
                    <div id="node-2" class="node clear-block">


  
  <div class="content">
    <p>You can also find me on <strong><a href="http://scholar.google.com/citations?user=7ZznynkAAAAJ" target="_blank">Google Scholar</a></strong>,&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Santanu_Sarma" target="_blank">ResearchGate</a></strong></p>
<p>	<strong>Journal Papers:</strong></p>
<p>	&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>
		N.Dutt, A. Jantsch, S.Sarma, &ldquo;Toward Smart Embedded Systems: A Self-aware System-On-Chip (SoC) Perspective,&rdquo; TECS, ACM,&nbsp;2016.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, S.Giridharlal, S.Udupa, K.Parameswaran, N.K. Malik, K.M. Bharadwaj, Prashant A R, B. S. Jagadesh Babu, S. Shankarnarayan, &nbsp;&ldquo;<a href="http://students.ics.uci.edu/~santanus/projects/jst-osde.pdf">A Digital Signal Processor based On-Board System for Structural Dynamic Studies and Experiments in Indian Geostationary Satellites,</a>&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>Journal of Spacecraft Technology</em>, Vol. 20, No. 2, pp.47-54, July 2010.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, and A. Venkateswarlu, &ldquo;Systematic Errors Cancellations and Fault Detection of Resolver Angular Sensors Using a DSP Based System,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>Mechatronics,</em>&nbsp;Elsevier Publications,Vol.19, No. 8, pp. 1303-1312, December 2009.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, V.K. Agrawal, and S. Udupa &ldquo;<a href="http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/abstractSimilar.jsp?arnumber=4387924">Software Based Resolver-to-Digital Conversion Using DSP</a>,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>IEEE Transactions on Industrial Electronics</em>, Vol. 55, No.1, pp.371-397, January 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, &ldquo;Frequency and phase locked loop using adaptive phase detectors,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>Australian Journal of Electrical &amp; Electronics Engineering,&nbsp;</em>Vol. 4, Issue 2, pp 135-145, 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, &ldquo;An adaptive synchronous amplitude demodulation technique in presence of systematic disturbances for sensors and instrumentation applications,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>International Journal of Electronics and Communication</em>, Vol. 62, Issue 6, pp.438-444, June 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, S. Udupa, V.K. Agrawal, and K. Parameswaran &ldquo;Instantaneous angular position and speed measurement using a software based resolver-to-digital converter,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>Measurement</em>, Vol. 41, Issue 7, pp. 788-796,&nbsp; August 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, &ldquo;An Adaptive Nonlinear Filter (ANF) for Online Parameter Estimation of Undamped and Damped Sinusoids,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>Journal of Mechanical Systems and Signal Processing</em>, Vol. 21, Issue 2, pp.1026-1040, Feb. 2007.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, P. K. Maharana, and V.K. Agrawal, &ldquo;Flexible Mode Frequency Tracking Using Phase-Locked Loop,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>Journal of Spacecraft Technology</em>, Vol.14, No.2, pp.37-46, Bangalore, India, October 2004.</li>
</ol>
<p>	&nbsp;</p>
<p>	&nbsp;</p>
<p>	<strong>Conference Papers</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>
		S.Sarma, T. Muck, Luis Bathen, N.Dutt, A.Nicolau, &quot;SmartBalance: A Sensing-Driven Linux Load Balancer for Energy Efficiency of Heterogeneous MPSoCs&quot;, SF, DAC 2015.&nbsp;</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma,&nbsp;N.Venkatasubramanian, and&nbsp;N. Dutt, &quot;Sense-making from Distributed and Mobile Sensing Data: A Middleware Perspective&quot;,&nbsp;Proceedings of the 51st Design Automation Conference (DAC&#39;14), SF, CA, June 2014.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma and &nbsp;N.Dutt, &quot;Minimal Sparse Observability of Complex Networks: Application to MPSoC Sensor Placement and Run-time Thermal Estimation &amp; Tracking,&quot;&nbsp; Proceedings of the 17th Conference on Design, Automation and Test in Europe (DATE&#39;14), Dresden, Germany, 2014.&nbsp;</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, N. Dutt, N.Venkatasubramanian,A.Nicolau, and P.Gupta &quot;Cyberphysical-System-On-Chip (CPSoC): A Self-Aware Design Paradigm with Cross-Layer Virtual Sensors and Actuators,&quot; &nbsp; Design Automation Conference, DAC,2013, Work-In-Progress, Austin, Texas, 2013.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, N. Dutt, N.Venkatasubramanian, &quot;Cross-Layer Virtual Observers for Embedded Multiprocessor System-on-Chip (MPSoC),&quot; &nbsp;Adaptive and Reflective Middleware (ARM 2012)/ Middleware Conference,Montreal, Canada,&nbsp;&nbsp;Dec 3-7,&nbsp;2012.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma and N.Dutt, &quot;Energy and Performance-aware task scheduling in heterogeneous parallel platforms,&quot;&nbsp;<em>ACM SRC</em>,&nbsp;<em>Design Automation Conference</em>, DAC12, SF, June 2012.(Poster)</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, S.Udupa, K.Parameswaran, K.M.Bharadwaj, and N.K. Malik &ldquo;A hardware-software codesign approach to a JPEG encoder design for a planetary micro-rover application,&rdquo; <em>Intelligent Robots and Computer Vision XXVIII: Algorithms and Techniques</em>, Hyatt Regency Hotel, San Francisco Airport, California, USA, 2010.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, S.Udupa, K.Parameswaran, and K.M.Bharadwaj, &ldquo;Reconfigurable BPSK Modulation Scheme for Satellite Data Telemetry,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>World Congress on Engineering and Computer Science</em>, WCECS2010, San Francisco, USA, Oct. 2010.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma and J.K.Kishore, &ldquo;Simple Fault Detection and Identification Schemes for Resolver Angular Sensor,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>3rd MATEIT-2010</em>, New Delhi, India, January 2010.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, A. K. Kulkarni, A. Venkateswaralu, P. Natarajan, and N.K. Malik, &ldquo;Spacecraft Dynamics Modeling and Simulation Using Matlab-Simulink,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>3rd MATEIT-2010</em>, New Delhi, India, January 2010.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, S.Udupa, K.Parameshwaran, K.M Bharadwaj, and N. K Malik, &ldquo;Model Organization: An Effective Technique in Model Driven Development of On-board Software for Spacecraft Bus Management Unit&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>60th</em>&nbsp;<em>International Astronautical Congress,</em>&nbsp;Daejeon, Republic of Korea, October 2009.&nbsp;</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, K.Parameshwaran, V.K.Agrawal, and S.Udupa, &ldquo;Design and FPGA Implementation of Multiple Data Rate BPSK Modulation Scheme for Satellite Data Telemetry,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>2ndNational Conference on Mathematical Techniques: Emerging Paradigms for Electronics and IT Industries,</em>&nbsp;Delhi University, New Delhi, 2008.&nbsp;</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, V.K. Agrawal, K. Parameswaran, and S. Udupa &ldquo;ASIC Design of an On-Board Storage (OBS)Subsystem for Satellite Health Keeping Data Management and Telemetry,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>MATEIT</em>, Delhi University, New Delhi, India, 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma and V.K. Agrawal &ldquo;A Mixed-Signal Programmable SoC Architecture for Resolver-to-Digital Converter and Motor Control Applications Using CORDIC,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>National Conference on Emerging Trends and Advances in Electrical Engineering and&nbsp; Renewable Energy</em>,&nbsp;<em>NCEEERE</em>, Sikkim Manipal Institute of Technology, India, 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma,V.K. Agrawal, S.Udupa, and K.Parameswaran &ldquo;Distributed Control System Design Using MIL STD- 1553B Bus,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>WCIT-2008</em>, Vikram Sarabhai Space Centre, Trivendrum, India, Oct 2008.&nbsp;</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, S. Udupa, and V.K. Agrawal, &ldquo;Design and Implementation of a Java Based Application Software for Design Automation and Optimization of the Temperature Control System of Indian Satellites,&rdquo;<em>&nbsp;Conference on Advances in Space Science and Technology (CASST&rsquo;08),&nbsp;</em>IIT Kharagpur, January 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, Navle Sonal Giridharlal, S.Udupa, K Parameshwaran, V.K.Agrawal, &ldquo;A DSP Processor Based On-Board System Design for Vibration Senor Data Acquisition and Playback in GSAT-4 Spacecraft&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>59th</em>&nbsp;<em>International Astronautical Congress</em>,&nbsp;Glasgow, Scotland, 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma and V.K. Agrawal &ldquo;A Closed-Loop Quadrature Phase Detector for Phase and Frequency Discrimination along with Suppression of DC bias,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>Conference on Advances in Space Science and Technology (CASST&rsquo;08),&nbsp;</em>IIT Kharagpur, January 2008.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma and V.K. Agrawal &ldquo;Online Methods for Joint Estimation of Time Delay and Doppler Shift,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>58th International Astronautical Congress,&nbsp;</em>IAC-07-B2.2, Hyderabad, India, September 2007.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, S. Udupa, V.K. Agrawal, and K. Parameswaran &ldquo;Software System Architecture Modeling Using UML,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>58th</em>&nbsp;<em>International Astronautical Congress,</em>&nbsp;IAC-07-D1.3.10, Hyderabad, India, September 2007.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, P. K. Maharana, and V.K. Agrawal, &ldquo;Phase-Locked Loop Design for Flexible Mode Tracking,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>IEEE</em><em>&nbsp;TENCON 2003. Conference on Convergent Technologies for Asia-Pacific Region</em>, Vol. 4,&nbsp;pp 1277 &ndash; 1283, 15-17 Oct. 2003.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma and S.Majhi, &ldquo;Design and Implementation of Digital Controller Using Subband Coding,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>Proceedings of International Conference on Intelligent Control System and Signal Processing (ICONS)</em>, Ferro, Portugal, April 2003.</li>
<li>
		S.Sarma, S.Majhi, and A.K.Gogoi, &ldquo;Digital Controller Implementation Using Block Digital Filtering,&rdquo;&nbsp;<em>IEEE proceedings of the International Conference on Control Applications</em>, Vol. 2, pp. 892-896, Glasgow, Scotland, September 2002.</li>
</ol>
